WEBVTT

00:13.430 --> 00:14.290
Please come in.

00:20.510 --> 00:21.440
Grand Tutor, this is who

00:21.440 --> 00:25.100
you've been meaning to meet,
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin.

00:28.120 --> 00:31.760
Your Majesty has finally
shown your true face.

00:34.560 --> 00:35.840
I have no choice.

00:38.070 --> 00:40.400
Young Lord Xiao has seen right through me.

00:40.560 --> 00:41.760
Any more concealment

00:42.280 --> 00:43.540
would be meaningless.

00:44.280 --> 00:45.670
Your Majesty feels unwell,

00:45.670 --> 00:48.520
yet you are still personally
hosting the peace talks.

00:48.520 --> 00:49.880
It is never easy to be a mother.

00:49.880 --> 00:51.390
My end is drawing near.

00:52.600 --> 00:55.860
I have to settle certain matters myself
before my passing.

00:56.470 --> 00:57.670
This trip of mine is

00:58.710 --> 00:59.750
partly

01:00.240 --> 01:01.640
for an old acquantaince,

01:02.150 --> 01:03.350
and partly

01:04.280 --> 01:05.870
for you, Grand Tutor Xie.

01:13.070 --> 01:15.350
Haven't you always been wondering

01:17.120 --> 01:20.070
about the truth of the gruesome case
where the An and Lu families

01:20.070 --> 01:23.070
colluded with the enemy
and allied with the Northern Qin's

01:23.070 --> 01:24.200
Right King of Virtue

01:24.310 --> 01:27.840
from the Mulian family
to establish their own administration?

01:29.760 --> 01:31.960
I had not yet entered the palace by then.

01:32.039 --> 01:34.300
Some things are not easy to investigate.

01:34.590 --> 01:35.509
That said, I am

01:36.560 --> 01:39.220
willing to cooperate with you,
Grand Tutor Xie.

01:39.280 --> 01:41.070
Didn't Your Majesty just say

01:41.509 --> 01:43.430
that your end is drawing near?

01:43.759 --> 01:45.160
Do you think cooperation

01:45.560 --> 01:47.160
is impossible when I am dead?

01:50.759 --> 01:51.950
It is not true.

01:52.950 --> 01:54.039
Only when I am dead

01:54.430 --> 01:55.890
can the two of us cooperate

01:56.870 --> 01:58.560
on some issues.

03:33.360 --> 03:36.940
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

03:37.110 --> 03:39.870
[Episode 12]

03:42.720 --> 03:44.670
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

03:46.120 --> 03:47.630
Don't be so petty.

03:47.840 --> 03:49.650
I know this workshop
belongs to Yuan Xiaoliu.

03:49.650 --> 03:51.380
I'm just borrowing it for a bit.

03:51.400 --> 03:52.460
Frankly speaking,

03:52.470 --> 03:53.870
this looks quite like the one at my home.

03:53.870 --> 03:56.150
Don't all workshops look similar?

03:56.960 --> 03:57.710
Wait, who told you

03:57.710 --> 03:58.750
this was meant for Yuan Xiaoliu?

03:58.750 --> 04:00.280
So this is not his workshop?

04:01.280 --> 04:02.810
How could he charge me rent?

04:07.960 --> 04:08.760
Explain this.

04:09.590 --> 04:10.680
It's about a private job I took

04:10.680 --> 04:11.870
at the Miraculous Craft shop.

04:11.870 --> 04:13.470
The well in Honglu Temple was clogged,

04:13.470 --> 04:14.600
so I went to clear it.

04:18.800 --> 04:19.510
What about this?

04:19.510 --> 04:21.000
This is for cracking sunflower seeds.

04:21.000 --> 04:22.600
Look, just turn it like this,

04:23.070 --> 04:24.930
and a load of seeds can be cracked.

04:27.240 --> 04:28.870
This copper ball here contains fragrances.

04:28.870 --> 04:30.560
Didn't you say the people of Northern Qin
eat strong-smelling food,

04:30.560 --> 04:31.430
and thus have noticeable body odors?

04:31.430 --> 04:32.430
If they carry this around,

04:32.430 --> 04:33.630
their odors can be covered,

04:33.630 --> 04:35.680
and the pleasant scent in it
will last for several months.

04:35.680 --> 04:38.159
Did you still plan to blow up
the Eagle King with fire thunderstones?

04:38.159 --> 04:39.090
Definitely not.

04:40.240 --> 04:40.830
I...

04:42.159 --> 04:43.720
Who said I went see him?

04:43.720 --> 04:44.450
That's a lie.

04:45.000 --> 04:45.930
Keep lying then.

04:46.600 --> 04:48.070
Didn't you go to meet the Eagle King

04:48.070 --> 04:49.130
for Li Lejun today?

04:50.190 --> 04:52.730
Tell me. What did you promise
to give the Eagle King in exchange

04:52.730 --> 04:54.790
for halting the political marriage?

04:55.310 --> 04:55.950
Spill it.

04:57.930 --> 04:59.190
Repeating crossbows?

05:00.160 --> 05:00.920
Gunpowder?

05:17.120 --> 05:17.800
Xie Jiayu,

05:18.560 --> 05:19.690
tell me what this is.

05:20.160 --> 05:20.870
Don't hit me in the face!

05:20.870 --> 05:22.070
This is refined iron.

05:22.120 --> 05:24.180
And this is your so-called solution?

05:24.560 --> 05:26.620
Do you even know this will have you...

05:27.660 --> 05:28.720
You're such a fool.

05:31.270 --> 05:33.720
I didn't trade the iron casting technique
to the Eagle King.

05:33.720 --> 05:34.980
Please say something!

05:35.040 --> 05:36.680
I really didn't betray Ye.

05:36.870 --> 05:38.510
I know sometimes
I can be a bit unreliable,

05:38.510 --> 05:40.570
but I'd never cross the line, would I?

05:42.240 --> 05:43.800
Fine. Believe what you want.

05:43.800 --> 05:44.480
Alright?

05:44.630 --> 05:45.820
The Eagle King agreed to set Lejun free

05:45.820 --> 05:47.430
if I offered
the iron casting technique.

05:47.430 --> 05:48.690
Are you satisfied now?

05:51.000 --> 05:52.630
What exactly are you mad about?

05:52.630 --> 05:53.120
I already told you

05:53.120 --> 05:54.480
I didn't sell out
the iron casting technique.

05:54.480 --> 05:56.680
I was merely selling
devices of my own creation.

05:56.680 --> 05:58.010
What do you mean by this?

05:58.170 --> 06:01.310
Your Highness, have you ever heard about
the Miraculous Craft?

06:01.310 --> 06:02.160
No, never.

06:03.240 --> 06:05.870
This Brilliant Manual on Farm Tools
records

06:06.190 --> 06:07.520
all the farm implements

06:07.560 --> 06:10.310
designed and improved
by the Miraculous Craft, namely me.

06:10.310 --> 06:12.560
Please look at this foot-treadled
water diversion tool.

06:12.560 --> 06:14.310
By replacing the straight shaft
with a curved one

06:14.310 --> 06:15.510
and adding three fans,

06:15.510 --> 06:17.070
it can be used to easily reclaim
a hundred mu

06:17.070 --> 06:18.430
of alkaline earth as farmland a day

06:18.430 --> 06:20.430
even in the northern desert region.

06:24.000 --> 06:25.310
And this dragon-bone water-lifting device

06:25.310 --> 06:27.190
combines the wisdom of the chapter
on waterways in the Record of Trades.

06:27.190 --> 06:28.680
It saves much manpower.

06:28.680 --> 06:30.800
With it, even an 80-year-old woman

06:30.800 --> 06:32.680
can clear over 70 mu of wasteland.

06:33.430 --> 06:35.240
Here's a bird-shaped bronze rain gauge.

06:35.240 --> 06:36.750
The beak is filled with saltpeter,

06:36.750 --> 06:38.159
while the tail is inlaid with a compass.

06:38.159 --> 06:39.720
Blue smoke is guaranteed to appear

06:39.720 --> 06:41.580
three days before an earthquake.

06:46.000 --> 06:47.290
Sweet sorghum can be planted
in the southern desert area,

06:47.290 --> 06:49.190
and cold-region mulberry trees
on Mount Yin,

06:49.190 --> 06:51.510
with the help
of iron-rimmed wooden ploughing wheels.

06:51.510 --> 06:55.390
This page instructs on how to turn
saline-alkali land into fertile fields.

06:55.390 --> 06:58.790
Can Your Highness bear to watch
the manual burned into ashes?

06:59.900 --> 07:00.340
You!

07:01.480 --> 07:01.920
You...

07:01.920 --> 07:04.450
Don't worry.
I've memorized all the content.

07:05.950 --> 07:07.720
Although Northern Qin
has occupied the Capital,

07:07.720 --> 07:10.150
your people are good at nomadism,
not farming.

07:10.150 --> 07:12.190
Last year, 30,000 head cattle and sheep
died from the cold.

07:12.190 --> 07:14.020
The harvest in the fields were poor.

07:14.020 --> 07:15.870
The national treasury
had few grain reserves.

07:15.870 --> 07:17.160
The people of Northern Qin

07:17.160 --> 07:18.890
endured quite a bitter winter.

07:19.800 --> 07:20.480
But now,

07:20.950 --> 07:23.010
I can help you break the constraints.

07:23.070 --> 07:25.670
As long as you call off
the marriage to Li Lejun,

07:26.390 --> 07:28.430
I'll gift you all the instruments

07:28.800 --> 07:30.760
in the Brilliant Manual on Farm Tools.

07:30.760 --> 07:31.760
What do you think?

07:34.630 --> 07:35.690
Are all of these...

07:36.800 --> 07:38.310
really your inventions?

07:39.720 --> 07:41.920
Yes, I am exactly the Miraculous Craft.

07:45.680 --> 07:46.600
I understand

07:46.680 --> 07:47.310
that the superior quality

07:47.310 --> 07:49.050
of Beifu Army's weaponry
is based on the iron casting technique.

07:49.050 --> 07:49.830
I simply used it a pretext

07:49.830 --> 07:51.960
to lure the Eagle King into meeting me.

07:54.240 --> 07:55.300
Xiao Wuyi, listen.

07:55.430 --> 07:56.240
I swear,

07:56.430 --> 07:58.190
if I had truly traded
the smelting technique for refined iron

07:58.190 --> 07:59.120
to the Eagle King,

07:59.120 --> 07:59.920
fate would have it

07:59.920 --> 08:00.950
that I get trafficked again
when I leave Jiankang

08:00.950 --> 08:02.040
-and...
-Do you need a fix

08:02.040 --> 08:03.300
on that mouth of yours?

08:03.510 --> 08:05.510
Can't you stop saying unlucky things?

08:05.510 --> 08:06.430
I was just trying

08:06.430 --> 08:07.960
to express my loyalty to Ye.

08:08.310 --> 08:10.240
You have no idea what I'm mad about.

08:11.000 --> 08:12.120
Tell me then.

08:12.270 --> 08:13.270
You shouldn't have shown your abilities

08:13.270 --> 08:14.730
in front of the Eagle King.

08:15.390 --> 08:17.310
Techniques are dead, but people are alive.

08:17.310 --> 08:18.240
Have you ever considered

08:18.240 --> 08:19.190
what will happen

08:19.190 --> 08:20.630
if the Eagle King targets you?

08:20.630 --> 08:22.270
Aren't you planning to explore the world?

08:22.270 --> 08:23.560
When I get to the Northern Border,

08:23.560 --> 08:24.480
I'll be too far away to help you.

08:24.480 --> 08:25.510
Should there be slight negligence

08:25.510 --> 08:27.070
or even just an opportunity,

08:27.070 --> 08:29.120
he can capture you
and take you to Northern Qin.

08:29.120 --> 08:30.950
Then you won't have anyone to turn to.

08:30.950 --> 08:32.789
You're not exactly the brave type.

08:32.789 --> 08:34.120
When your life is in the palm of his hand,

08:34.120 --> 08:36.450
will you ever refuse to do
what he asks you?

08:40.669 --> 08:42.480
Well, Mao's always there for me.

08:42.789 --> 08:44.120
He can protect me too.

08:51.230 --> 08:51.750
Indeed,

08:52.870 --> 08:54.670
there is someone to protect you.

08:55.240 --> 08:57.240
I shouldn't have worried about you.

09:25.350 --> 09:27.230
The first thing you need is a lesson

09:27.230 --> 09:28.830
on how to intimidate others.

09:29.270 --> 09:30.130
In this regard,

09:30.480 --> 09:32.680
Xiao Wuyi has set a good example for you.

09:35.000 --> 09:36.330
Whether to stay or leave

09:37.390 --> 09:38.240
is up to you.

09:44.040 --> 09:45.370
Take good care of Lejun.

09:50.610 --> 09:53.200
[Cui Mansion]

09:55.850 --> 09:57.910
[Cui Xi, butler of the Cui Mansion]

09:56.630 --> 09:58.870
Greetings, Your Highness.

10:02.670 --> 10:03.800
Just bury this woman

10:04.000 --> 10:06.800
who thought she was Princess Qi
somewhere random.

10:09.000 --> 10:10.630
I request a audience with Master Cui.

10:10.630 --> 10:12.500
No need to enter the premises,
Your Highness.

10:12.500 --> 10:13.690
Master Cui will not

10:14.830 --> 10:15.960
meet Your Highness.

10:18.200 --> 10:19.130
Get out of my way.

10:21.390 --> 10:24.000
Would you take a look at this,
Your Highness?

10:24.440 --> 10:26.170
Master Cui knew perfectly well

10:26.440 --> 10:28.480
that Your Highness
would surely pay a visit

10:28.480 --> 10:31.510
for the political marriage
arranged for Princess Pingning.

10:31.510 --> 10:34.640
So, he insisted that I pass on a message
to Your Highness,

10:35.080 --> 10:38.340
hoping that you would
put the national interests above all

10:38.560 --> 10:40.420
and prioritize the greater good.

10:42.390 --> 10:43.520
I must see Master Cui

10:43.750 --> 10:45.280
for an urgent matter today.

10:45.550 --> 10:47.350
Please do lend me a helping hand.

10:52.120 --> 10:54.200
Your Highness, have some self-respect!

10:54.200 --> 10:56.550
Do you even know this is the Cui Mansion?

10:57.060 --> 10:58.520
Is Your Highness trying to

10:58.670 --> 11:01.930
ruin the Cui family's good reputation
by offering bribes?

11:05.080 --> 11:06.240
I do address you as Your Highness,

11:06.240 --> 11:09.230
but do you really think
you're some precious Prince Qi?

11:09.230 --> 11:10.990
Even Qizhou is long gone—

11:11.870 --> 11:16.120
Princess Qi was no better
than a stray dog, was she?

11:17.080 --> 11:18.320
Mother!

11:17.600 --> 11:19.540
[Young Li Lejun]
[Young Li Mao]

11:18.790 --> 11:20.550
Mother...

11:21.480 --> 11:22.410
What did you say?

11:22.670 --> 11:23.120
I said...

11:23.120 --> 11:23.750
Answer me!

11:25.960 --> 11:27.160
What did you just say?

11:29.930 --> 11:31.530
Well, actually, I didn't...

11:35.000 --> 11:35.870
I am the Regent now.

11:35.870 --> 11:37.270
Step forward, I dare you!

11:39.150 --> 11:40.270
Years ago, Empress Wenxi

11:40.270 --> 11:41.800
was incomparably capable.

11:42.120 --> 11:45.840
She single-handedly helped the nobles
migrate to the south safely.

11:45.840 --> 11:47.640
How come the nowadays Cui family

11:48.390 --> 11:50.550
is filled with selfish and cowardly gits

11:50.550 --> 11:52.030
terrified of death?

11:59.440 --> 12:00.900
A dignified royal pincess

12:01.230 --> 12:03.760
was given away to the rebels
by the Cui family.

12:12.560 --> 12:13.260
Stop!

12:14.670 --> 12:16.200
It was a misunderstanding.

12:20.220 --> 12:21.480
What's wrong with you?

12:22.410 --> 12:25.070
This is Prince Qi, the current Regent.

12:22.610 --> 12:24.840
[Chief Clerk Cui,
master of the Cui family]

12:25.320 --> 12:27.450
How dare you disrespect His Highness?

12:27.550 --> 12:28.750
Have you completely forgotten

12:28.750 --> 12:30.480
the etiquette observed by the Cui family?

12:30.480 --> 12:31.550
-I…
-Go away!

12:31.550 --> 12:32.200
Yes.

12:36.750 --> 12:38.080
Your Highness is paying

12:38.910 --> 12:43.310
this visit for the political marriage
arranged for Princess Pingning, right?

12:47.030 --> 12:50.440
I know Your Highness can't bear to see
the princess marry far away.

12:50.440 --> 12:53.500
But this political marriage
is a major matter of state.

12:56.120 --> 12:58.720
The Cui family alone
cannot interfere with it.

13:00.960 --> 13:03.630
Do you mean the Cui family won't help me?

13:04.720 --> 13:06.450
It's not that we refuse to help.

13:06.960 --> 13:09.560
It's just that we're unable
to render any help.

13:10.000 --> 13:10.860
Your Highness,

13:11.390 --> 13:13.960
letting Princess Pingning get married
for political purposes

13:13.960 --> 13:15.080
could actually be

13:15.440 --> 13:17.120
a good thing for you.

13:22.790 --> 13:24.650
Was Cangfeng Forge built for you?

13:24.690 --> 13:25.560
Are you in charge now?

13:25.560 --> 13:26.010
No...

13:26.080 --> 13:27.360
Did anyone say
you could lend it to Xie Jiayu?

13:27.360 --> 13:28.360
You even charged her rent.

13:28.360 --> 13:29.030
What now?

13:30.150 --> 13:31.670
Kicking me to the curb after using me,
huh?

13:31.670 --> 13:34.390
Let me ask you.
Who exerted his utmost effort

13:34.390 --> 13:35.240
and racked his brains

13:35.240 --> 13:37.100
to help you keep that girl around?

13:37.320 --> 13:39.150
So you taught Xie Jiayu
how to smelt for refined iron.

13:39.150 --> 13:40.600
Did I tell you to do that?

13:42.240 --> 13:43.120
She made it.

13:43.390 --> 13:44.200
So soon?

13:44.790 --> 13:45.720
How very gifted.

13:46.270 --> 13:47.400
She's a rare genius.

13:47.630 --> 13:49.120
Xiao Wuyi, listen.

13:49.390 --> 13:51.320
You must do whatever it takes to...

13:54.240 --> 13:56.150
This is not entirely my fault.

13:57.440 --> 13:59.240
I simply gave her a rough idea.

14:00.480 --> 14:01.340
Your Highness.

14:01.910 --> 14:03.770
Prince Qi went to the Cui Mansion.

14:04.110 --> 14:05.370
What is he doing there?

14:05.830 --> 14:08.750
[Cui Mansion]

14:28.390 --> 14:29.120
How did it go?

14:30.440 --> 14:32.470
Did Chief Clerk Cui say yes?

14:43.510 --> 14:44.310
Let's go home.

14:45.030 --> 14:45.600
Master,

14:47.080 --> 14:48.680
I'd like to take a walk alone.

14:56.670 --> 14:57.930
Protect His Highness.

14:58.010 --> 14:58.770
-Yes.
-Yes.

15:03.680 --> 15:04.740
Hurry, over there!

15:05.120 --> 15:06.600
We'd better not be late.

15:07.150 --> 15:08.550
This is truly a noble good deed.

15:08.550 --> 15:11.390
Princess Pingning is marrying
into Northern Qin to safeguard Ye.

15:11.390 --> 15:13.120
The imperial court plans to build
a monument for her.

15:13.120 --> 15:14.270
I'll lead the fundraising!

15:14.270 --> 15:14.960
I'm going with you!

15:14.960 --> 15:16.030
- Let's go!
- Let's go!

15:16.030 --> 15:17.560
-Let's all go!
-Count me in!

15:18.690 --> 15:19.550
Hurry up!

15:19.550 --> 15:21.000
-This is my share.
-Come, guys!

15:21.000 --> 15:22.080
And this is my share.

15:22.080 --> 15:22.720
Count me in!

15:22.720 --> 15:23.600
This is my share.

15:23.080 --> 15:25.550
[Raising funds to repay the princess
for protecting Ye]

15:23.870 --> 15:24.720
This is my share!

15:24.720 --> 15:26.720
Take it all. I'm offering this much.

15:26.790 --> 15:27.920
And here is my share.

15:28.000 --> 15:28.790
Count me in!

15:28.910 --> 15:29.870
Smash this place.

15:29.870 --> 15:30.870
We're also here to contribute.

15:30.870 --> 15:32.150
No pushing, please!

15:32.150 --> 15:33.080
This is my share.

15:33.600 --> 15:35.000
I said, smash this place!

15:37.720 --> 15:38.390
Go away!

15:40.240 --> 15:41.440
No donation allowed!

15:42.600 --> 15:43.270
Scram!

15:45.000 --> 15:47.270
Grandma!

15:48.000 --> 15:49.840
Grandma...

16:07.630 --> 16:10.090
It was who ordered them
to break up the crowd.

16:13.870 --> 16:14.480
Yizhi,

16:15.720 --> 16:17.240
you shouldn't do things like that.

16:17.240 --> 16:18.440
Then what should I do?

16:22.390 --> 16:23.870
You hit a man in the Cui Mansion?

16:23.870 --> 16:24.320
Yes.

16:26.510 --> 16:28.110
But I didn't feel pain at all.

16:28.360 --> 16:29.790
It actually gave me a thrill.

16:29.790 --> 16:32.190
I should have beaten him to death
years ago.

16:37.000 --> 16:38.600
When a man carries no weapon,

16:39.150 --> 16:41.210
he can only fight with his bare hands.

16:41.480 --> 16:42.870
That said, I'm also aware

16:42.870 --> 16:44.000
there is only one way

16:45.030 --> 16:46.830
to persuade the noble families.

16:48.250 --> 16:49.910
Let's bond through marriage.

16:49.960 --> 16:51.290
Lingyi of the Cui family

16:51.600 --> 16:52.600
is a noble lady.

16:53.750 --> 16:55.240
Having grown up as a bright child,

16:55.240 --> 16:56.640
she is elegant in manners

16:58.030 --> 17:00.630
and refined
in both appearance and character.

17:02.270 --> 17:04.329
I swear to resort to any means to unite

17:04.640 --> 17:05.920
all the major noble families

17:05.920 --> 17:08.170
to fight for a chance
to get Your Highness and Princess Pingning

17:08.170 --> 17:09.589
out of the current quagmire.

17:09.589 --> 17:11.160
From this day onward, we the Cui family

17:11.160 --> 17:13.690
pledge to stand together
with Your Highness.

17:14.109 --> 17:15.569
Were there dangers ahead,

17:15.880 --> 17:18.280
we would not hesitate
to aid Your Highness.

17:23.030 --> 17:24.550
That day before the palace gate,

17:24.550 --> 17:26.430
I misspoke in a moment of desperation.

17:26.430 --> 17:28.270
I know you have your own difficulties.

17:28.270 --> 17:29.920
But since I am the Regent now,

17:30.150 --> 17:31.830
I shouldn't rely on you
to help my own sister

17:31.830 --> 17:32.880
out of trouble.

17:34.640 --> 17:36.040
I will use my own strength

17:36.360 --> 17:38.290
to protect those I want to protect.

17:38.310 --> 17:41.040
I will also continue
to promote reforms with you.

17:41.200 --> 17:42.590
Then what about Xie Jiayu?

17:42.590 --> 17:44.190
I'll leave the choice to her.

17:46.000 --> 17:47.660
With Yaoyao's devotion to me,

17:47.860 --> 17:49.440
I'm sure she will stick around.

17:49.440 --> 17:50.790
But you just proposed to marry Ms. Cui.

17:50.790 --> 17:51.510
So what?

17:52.960 --> 17:55.750
Wuyi, when you asked for
Yaoyao's hand in marriage,

17:55.750 --> 17:57.480
didn't you already have a wife?

17:57.790 --> 17:59.510
We both had to adopt expedients, right?

17:59.510 --> 18:01.440
How could you compare your situation
with mine?

18:01.440 --> 18:03.440
Xie Jiayu and I used to be strangers.

18:03.510 --> 18:04.840
What's the difference?

18:04.880 --> 18:05.830
I asked to marry Ms. Cui

18:05.830 --> 18:07.430
only to save Lejun, didn't I?

18:07.510 --> 18:08.440
Yaoyao loves me.

18:08.510 --> 18:10.240
She will surely understand me.

18:10.870 --> 18:11.740
Li Yizhi,

18:13.160 --> 18:15.220
you're even a worse bastard than I am.

18:18.480 --> 18:19.280
You're right.

18:20.880 --> 18:21.920
If being a good person

18:21.920 --> 18:23.880
only turns me into a pawn,

18:28.200 --> 18:29.790
I'd rather be a villain.

19:15.750 --> 19:16.720
Someone said

19:16.880 --> 19:18.110
she'd like to forge

19:18.110 --> 19:19.840
an unparalleled sword for you.

19:20.110 --> 19:21.750
It must be extraordinarily sharp

19:21.750 --> 19:23.880
and can be used as a saber.

19:24.510 --> 19:26.790
It also has to be a hundred times better

19:26.790 --> 19:28.110
than the Eagle King's Longque Blade.

19:28.110 --> 19:31.310
So, she asked me to teach her
how to smelt for refined iron.

19:31.310 --> 19:34.590
I just didn't know how to decline
her request.

19:36.920 --> 19:38.580
What took you so long to say it?

19:44.380 --> 19:45.440
Where is Xie Jiayu?

19:45.880 --> 19:47.240
Since the Young Lady's departure
earlier today,

19:47.240 --> 19:49.900
she has not returned
to Wensheng Courtyard yet.

20:03.160 --> 20:03.820
This is bad.

20:22.270 --> 20:23.590
Are you literally crying

20:23.590 --> 20:25.030
because I scolded you a bit?

20:25.030 --> 20:26.350
You almost exposed my military secrets,

20:26.350 --> 20:28.550
and I haven't held you accountable yet.

20:35.890 --> 20:38.690
Did you... temper with
my portrait of a noble lady?

20:39.300 --> 20:40.020
You...

20:40.810 --> 20:42.070
As the dignified general of Beifu

20:42.070 --> 20:43.550
and the Heir of Prince Jing'an,

20:43.550 --> 20:45.810
you appear to keep a distance from women,

20:45.920 --> 20:48.000
but you're in fact stashing
a portrait of a noble lady.

20:48.000 --> 20:49.200
You have no scruples.

20:52.490 --> 20:53.310
How is it any of your business?

20:53.310 --> 20:54.770
I am condemning you for...

20:56.050 --> 20:57.570
for your future darling.

21:00.000 --> 21:01.660
If there really is such a girl,

21:03.240 --> 21:04.440
let her do it herself.

21:14.350 --> 21:14.960
Hold on.

21:17.550 --> 21:18.750
Swords and blades are used by people.

21:18.750 --> 21:19.830
Shouldn't the length and form

21:19.830 --> 21:20.790
be designed based on

21:20.790 --> 21:22.650
the user's height and arm length?

21:23.110 --> 21:24.240
Look at this sloppy draft.

21:24.240 --> 21:25.510
Did you even put your heart into it?

21:25.510 --> 21:26.910
Why are you so demanding?

21:28.640 --> 21:30.680
Is this how the Miraculous Craft
does business?

21:30.680 --> 21:31.740
You're receiving a gift.

21:31.740 --> 21:32.720
Why so picky?

21:32.880 --> 21:34.030
This is just how I am.

21:34.400 --> 21:36.270
I only accept gifts that are to my liking.

21:36.270 --> 21:37.800
If not, don't give any to me.

21:39.270 --> 21:40.400
Reach out your arms.

21:42.620 --> 21:44.420
I don't have a tape measure here.

21:59.710 --> 22:02.440
♪ One glance from near stirs my heart ♪

22:02.660 --> 22:05.210
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

22:06.910 --> 22:10.920
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

22:11.090 --> 22:13.090
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

22:15.050 --> 22:18.050
♪ Sharing all the years together ♪

22:18.460 --> 22:22.830
♪ Peace I find nowhere but by your side ♪

22:23.420 --> 22:26.330
♪ Bear witness with our souls ♪

22:26.400 --> 22:28.920
Your hairband surely has many uses.

22:27.260 --> 22:30.720
♪ Fear no partings or wax and wane ♪

22:29.200 --> 22:29.720
Yes.

22:30.200 --> 22:31.110
It kills, too.

22:37.240 --> 22:38.750
If you don't want to be taken
by the Eagle King

22:38.750 --> 22:40.480
to Northern Qin for hard labor,

22:40.890 --> 22:42.070
then don't slack off anymore
during your practice

22:42.070 --> 22:43.930
of lightness skills with Yan Yue.

22:44.400 --> 22:47.530
At least, they can help you escape
when you get in danger.

22:47.720 --> 22:48.920
Thanks to these skills,

22:48.920 --> 22:50.270
you'll be able to go anywhere alone

22:50.270 --> 22:51.330
in this vast world.

22:59.440 --> 23:00.640
The visiting delegation

23:00.640 --> 23:02.920
includes the Empress Dowager
of Northern Qin.

23:02.920 --> 23:04.720
She and the Eagle King
are after different benefits.

23:04.720 --> 23:06.880
It's easier to halt the political marriage
through her.

23:06.880 --> 23:08.350
But before the peace talks complete,

23:08.350 --> 23:10.070
and the Eagle King leaves Jiankang,

23:10.070 --> 23:11.870
you'd better stay away from him.

23:12.430 --> 23:13.290
Did you hear me?

23:14.160 --> 23:15.090
Yes, I heard you.

23:15.500 --> 23:17.700
You're so nagging, just like my mother.

23:22.880 --> 23:23.810
I want to see Mao.

23:29.070 --> 23:29.730
No problem.

23:31.310 --> 23:32.570
I'll tell him about it.

23:56.790 --> 23:57.550
My Lady, isn't Mount Ya

23:57.550 --> 23:58.960
the place that Prince Qi yearns

23:58.960 --> 24:00.020
to go with you most?

24:00.110 --> 24:01.310
Why is it crossed out?

24:05.510 --> 24:06.510
Mao probably

24:07.790 --> 24:09.160
won't go there with me.

24:09.750 --> 24:11.830
My Lady, don't be upset.

24:12.590 --> 24:14.000
I'll always be with you.

24:16.880 --> 24:19.680
I think I'm feeling something
other than sadness.

24:20.070 --> 24:23.200
Do you remember that trip
along the river with lanterns?

24:24.070 --> 24:26.640
We wrote our wishes on small paper boats
at that time.

24:26.640 --> 24:28.110
I took a peek at Mao's.

24:28.400 --> 24:29.350
He wrote

24:30.070 --> 24:33.200
that he hoped Lejun and Yaoyao's wishes
would come true.

24:34.110 --> 24:36.440
Prince Qi has always been a nice gentleman

24:36.640 --> 24:39.440
who cares deeply
about you and Princess Pingning.

24:39.720 --> 24:40.850
But he seems to never

24:41.070 --> 24:43.130
really have anything he truly wants.

24:43.640 --> 24:44.590
I decided to run away from marriage,

24:44.590 --> 24:45.720
and he went with me.

24:46.310 --> 24:48.030
Even though he has become the Regent,

24:48.030 --> 24:50.560
he's ready to leave with me
as long as I want to.

24:52.160 --> 24:54.090
But it seems I've never figured out

24:54.160 --> 24:56.020
what Mao truly wants for himself.

24:56.350 --> 24:57.150
My Lady,

24:57.920 --> 24:59.850
what do you want for yourself then?

25:19.110 --> 25:20.920
Xiao Wuyi treats you really well.

25:20.920 --> 25:22.240
You're not related to him or anything,

25:22.240 --> 25:23.350
yet he especially built a workshop

25:23.350 --> 25:24.810
for you in his own mansion.

25:27.200 --> 25:28.350
It's midnight. Why did you

25:28.350 --> 25:30.070
come here instead of sleeping?

25:30.070 --> 25:30.870
I can't sleep.

25:31.350 --> 25:33.750
Hearing the sounds here
can soothe my mind.

25:43.240 --> 25:44.550
This is a military secret.

25:44.550 --> 25:47.030
You want to see it?
Ask me to be your master first.

25:47.030 --> 25:48.110
As if I care.

25:48.440 --> 25:49.700
I can make that myself.

26:10.400 --> 26:11.860
Those are blue fireworks.

26:13.270 --> 26:15.590
Yuan Xiaoliu, I can't believe you know
how to make blue fireworks.

26:15.590 --> 26:17.250
I've never seen these before.

26:17.480 --> 26:19.470
The books only say
that seashells make red fireworks,

26:19.470 --> 26:20.720
refined salt, yellow,

26:20.720 --> 26:21.790
silver powder, white,

26:21.790 --> 26:22.960
and azurite, green.

26:23.000 --> 26:24.260
But blue fireworks...

26:25.070 --> 26:27.110
Yuan Xiaoliu, you are amazing.

26:27.830 --> 26:29.440
How come I never noticed it before?

26:29.440 --> 26:30.200
Blue fireworks

26:30.200 --> 26:32.060
were a plaything in my childhood.

26:32.170 --> 26:33.680
It is also the first type of fireworks

26:33.680 --> 26:34.880
I've ever made in my life.

26:34.880 --> 26:36.030
How do I compare to you?

26:36.030 --> 26:37.160
You're impressive.

26:37.270 --> 26:38.720
But I just won't ask you to be my master.

26:38.720 --> 26:40.050
What can you do about it?

27:00.510 --> 27:02.160
Why not use the lightness skills
I taught you?

27:02.160 --> 27:03.550
Add two more sandbags to the training,

27:03.550 --> 27:04.700
and practice for four more hours tomorrow.

27:04.700 --> 27:05.560
Did you hear me?

27:06.880 --> 27:07.720
Yes, I got it.

27:07.830 --> 27:09.430
I won't be like this anymore.

27:10.510 --> 27:11.200
Take this.

27:23.640 --> 27:24.970
His Majesty is too soft,

27:25.160 --> 27:26.570
and shouldn't have agreed

27:26.570 --> 27:28.970
to grant Xiao Wuyi any time
to reform Beifu.

27:48.680 --> 27:51.480
I know you've never
approved of these peace talks.

27:51.590 --> 27:53.920
But if you hadn't underestimated the enemy

27:53.920 --> 27:55.920
and lost a battle at Jiuzhang Plain,

27:55.960 --> 27:57.110
these peace talks

27:57.830 --> 27:59.680
would probably be avoided.

28:03.720 --> 28:05.590
Given that the emperor is too young,

28:05.590 --> 28:07.110
and you're holding much military power,

28:07.110 --> 28:08.510
I demand you to promise me

28:08.640 --> 28:10.170
that even after my passing,

28:10.470 --> 28:13.000
you will still be of one mind
with the emperor.

28:15.270 --> 28:16.130
Yes, I promise.

28:25.420 --> 28:27.940
He really is hiding in Jiankang.

28:30.610 --> 28:31.410
Your Majesty.

28:33.680 --> 28:35.540
Where were the fireworks set off?

28:35.920 --> 28:36.830
Your Majesty,

28:37.120 --> 28:40.250
the fireworks were set off
in Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

28:43.520 --> 28:45.170
Xiao Wuyi...

28:49.200 --> 28:51.370
[Honglu Temple]

28:52.350 --> 28:53.540
I thought Your Majesty

28:53.540 --> 28:55.070
would never take my advice.

28:56.250 --> 28:58.140
I will, provided that you agree

28:58.590 --> 28:59.880
to find someone for me.

29:00.640 --> 29:01.240
Who is it?

29:01.550 --> 29:03.920
I saw a burst of blue fireworks
last night.

29:04.110 --> 29:06.830
That must be the work
of an old acquaintance of mine.

29:06.830 --> 29:07.960
Those fireworks...

29:08.200 --> 29:10.530
were set off in Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

29:13.400 --> 29:14.660
made by Mulian Ying...

29:16.520 --> 29:18.850
the very last survivor of the Mulian clan.

29:19.900 --> 29:21.900
I've spent 20 years looking for him.

29:22.270 --> 29:25.680
Little did I expect him
to be in your hands, Young Lord Xiao.

29:27.160 --> 29:28.200
Mulian Ying...

29:30.640 --> 29:32.280
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

29:36.640 --> 29:38.370
How did you come up with the idea

29:39.720 --> 29:41.780
of triggering the fuse with mercury?

29:43.480 --> 29:45.140
And you fancy being my master.

29:45.830 --> 29:47.000
Your fireworks suddenly exploded

29:47.000 --> 29:48.260
and almost injured me.

29:49.070 --> 29:51.730
Mercury is light in weight
and stable in nature.

29:52.200 --> 29:54.440
It won't kindle fire
no matter how you shake it.

29:54.440 --> 29:56.970
Besides, once the mechanism
is activated...

29:57.240 --> 29:57.960
Look.

30:00.440 --> 30:01.030
How is it?

30:01.030 --> 30:02.090
Ignited, isn't it?

30:04.550 --> 30:05.480
What's with you?

30:08.750 --> 30:09.440
Nothing.

30:10.000 --> 30:10.730
Impressive.

30:11.400 --> 30:13.440
You're way more talented than I am.

30:13.880 --> 30:14.740
You will surely

30:16.590 --> 30:18.520
become a legendary master one day.

30:19.920 --> 30:20.960
I am so flattered.

30:24.180 --> 30:26.240
You must take me as your master.

30:26.710 --> 30:27.710
If necessary,

30:27.730 --> 30:29.190
I can take you as my master.

30:29.270 --> 30:30.330
Then, the two of us,

30:30.400 --> 30:32.000
a duo of master and disciple,

30:32.270 --> 30:33.440
will work together to make

30:33.440 --> 30:35.440
an unparalleled caltrop fireball.

30:35.830 --> 30:37.070
In my mind right now,

30:37.440 --> 30:39.480
I'm already picturing us,

30:40.070 --> 30:42.550
as master and disciple,
leaving our mark in history.

30:42.550 --> 30:44.750
Come on, why is this act again?

30:44.920 --> 30:45.590
I helped you

30:45.590 --> 30:46.310
simply to honor

30:46.310 --> 30:47.640
my promise to Xiao Wuyi.

30:48.890 --> 30:50.720
He told me
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin

30:50.720 --> 30:52.720
saw the blue fireworks
we set off that night

30:52.720 --> 30:53.830
and liked them a lot.

30:53.830 --> 30:55.310
So she asked Xiao Wuyi to give her some

30:55.310 --> 30:56.910
to take back to Northern Qin.

30:58.880 --> 31:00.240
How could I let such an important gift

31:00.240 --> 31:02.240
for the peace talks easily explode?

31:06.400 --> 31:09.530
You just mentioned
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin?

31:12.400 --> 31:13.260
Do you know her?

31:14.370 --> 31:15.090
Me?

31:16.350 --> 31:19.810
How could I possibly know
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin?

31:20.160 --> 31:21.070
I mean,

31:21.070 --> 31:22.930
she holds such an exalted status.

31:23.830 --> 31:25.110
What brings her to this place?

31:25.110 --> 31:28.240
It's said that she's looking for
a man named Mulian Ying.

31:28.400 --> 31:29.960
Recently, Xiao Wuyi has also sent
Qing Long and Yan Yue

31:29.960 --> 31:31.220
to search for this man.

31:31.880 --> 31:33.340
When this person is found,

31:34.030 --> 31:36.830
the marriage arranged for Lejun
can be called off.

31:38.270 --> 31:40.810
Xiao Wuyi doesn't even know
who Mulian Ying is.

31:40.810 --> 31:42.470
How is he supposed to find him?

31:43.510 --> 31:46.110
I heard that he was given
a portrait of this man.

31:46.160 --> 31:48.690
It is how the man looked
as a teenager, though.

32:23.270 --> 32:26.310
The draft for the caltrop fireball
is beneath the stack.

32:26.310 --> 32:27.030
Oh, thanks.

32:28.480 --> 32:29.680
You were not fainted?

32:38.220 --> 32:39.480
You really are the man,

32:40.240 --> 32:41.070
Mulian Ying.

32:47.790 --> 32:51.190
The Empress Dowager of Northern Qin
has been looking for you.

32:54.480 --> 32:55.920
So you used me, Xiao Wuyi.

32:56.200 --> 32:59.060
You knew all along
that Yuan Xiaoliu is Mulian Ying.

33:01.000 --> 33:01.790
Xiao Wuyi,

33:02.310 --> 33:03.920
when did you find out who I am?

33:04.350 --> 33:05.400
On the day I saved you,

33:05.400 --> 33:07.160
I knew you were from Northern Qin.

33:07.160 --> 33:09.480
It just didn't cross my mind
that you're Mulian Ying.

33:09.480 --> 33:10.480
Over these years, the Northern Qin spies'

33:10.480 --> 33:11.880
top priority in Jiankang

33:12.240 --> 33:13.720
has always been finding Mulian Ying.

33:13.720 --> 33:17.050
The Empress Dowager of Northern Qin
is in Jiankang right now

33:17.200 --> 33:18.860
as a member of the delegation.

33:20.240 --> 33:23.590
Mulian Ying and I were once in love.

33:24.510 --> 33:28.030
However, the palace lanterns burn long,
casting light on the iron warrant.

33:28.030 --> 33:31.030
The bounds of the inner court
are like a moat to heaven.

33:31.200 --> 33:33.530
Despite all those great ambitions he had,

33:33.590 --> 33:36.190
the then emperor saw him
as a potential hazard.

33:36.270 --> 33:38.720
I thought I could at least keep him alive.

33:39.400 --> 33:40.460
But unexpectedly,

33:41.920 --> 33:45.050
I ended up causing
the destruction of his entirely clan.

33:47.480 --> 33:49.240
Being plagued by an old illness,

33:49.240 --> 33:50.700
my life is coming to an end.

33:51.680 --> 33:53.310
I hope you can find him for me,

33:53.670 --> 33:56.000
so I can see him one last time
before I pass,

33:58.270 --> 34:00.200
and clear up all these old grievances.

34:00.200 --> 34:01.400
What did you just say?

34:02.000 --> 34:03.480
What did you mean by
"her life is coming to an end"?

34:03.480 --> 34:04.400
If you are that worried,

34:04.400 --> 34:06.200
I will take you to see her directly.

34:06.200 --> 34:09.000
How do you know
if she's after Yuan Xiaoliu's life?

34:09.920 --> 34:10.710
Xiao Wuyi,

34:12.150 --> 34:13.949
are you doing this for yourself,

34:14.590 --> 34:15.630
or for me?

34:17.280 --> 34:19.880
I can not only help Li Lejun
regain her freedom,

34:20.320 --> 34:23.360
but also form an alliance

34:23.590 --> 34:27.389
between Northern Qin and Southern Ye
against the Eagle King's will,

34:27.750 --> 34:29.409
thus preventing years of war.

34:31.110 --> 34:33.400
What do you think, Young Lord Xiao?

34:34.550 --> 34:35.190
Xiao Wuyi,

34:35.800 --> 34:37.630
you promised me you'd help Lejun.

34:37.630 --> 34:38.710
Now the Empress Dowager
wants to see Yuan Xiaoliu.

34:38.710 --> 34:39.840
This is our only chance.

34:39.840 --> 34:41.770
No, I can't hand over Yuan Xiaoliu.

34:41.770 --> 34:43.370
This is a risk I will not take.

34:45.010 --> 34:46.340
I won't let her kill you,

34:47.230 --> 34:48.690
nor will I let you kill her.

34:50.440 --> 34:52.150
Over these years,
you've been hiding your identity

34:52.150 --> 34:53.670
and producing weapons in Beifu

34:53.670 --> 34:54.810
to fight Northern Qin.

34:54.810 --> 34:55.630
Isn't it because

34:55.630 --> 34:58.030
you're still holding hatred in your heart?

34:59.000 --> 35:00.150
Do you think she's asking to meet you

35:00.150 --> 35:02.150
just to do some catching up with you?

35:06.180 --> 35:06.980
Take him away.

35:24.070 --> 35:25.270
Go back to your place.

35:27.030 --> 35:28.630
I will figure something out.

35:28.630 --> 35:30.490
Is everything up for negotiation

35:30.880 --> 35:32.740
for your so-called greater good?

35:33.510 --> 35:34.910
And after being weighed,

35:35.440 --> 35:37.360
those who are hurt and sacrificed

35:37.360 --> 35:38.760
will always be us, right?

35:41.400 --> 35:43.270
The marriages arranged

35:43.630 --> 35:45.030
for me, Lejun,

35:46.880 --> 35:48.540
Sister Yuanji, and my mother,

35:49.440 --> 35:51.500
are about schemes and manipulation.

35:51.920 --> 35:53.580
Nobody cares about true love.

35:57.070 --> 35:58.470
If given another chance,

35:59.070 --> 36:00.190
you would still marry Ms. He

36:00.190 --> 36:01.650
for military provisions,

36:01.880 --> 36:03.190
ask the Empress Dowager
to grant a marriage

36:03.190 --> 36:04.960
so as to pressure Prince Changsha,

36:04.960 --> 36:05.760
and still place Lejun

36:05.760 --> 36:07.880
at the very end of all considerations.

36:07.880 --> 36:09.280
This is what you're like,

36:10.510 --> 36:11.480
Xiao Wuyi.

36:18.110 --> 36:18.920
Not just you,

36:20.510 --> 36:21.640
Mao has changed too.

36:22.760 --> 36:25.110
He already started selecting concubines
for himself.

36:25.110 --> 36:26.370
He has decided to stay,

36:27.800 --> 36:29.000
yet he hasn't told me.

36:30.760 --> 36:31.890
I'm well aware of it,

36:32.400 --> 36:33.600
but I'm still arguing

36:34.230 --> 36:36.890
relentlessly with you
about Lejun's marriage.

36:37.070 --> 36:39.270
You must be laughing at me in your heart.

36:42.920 --> 36:43.720
You are right.

36:44.880 --> 36:46.280
If given another chance,

36:48.400 --> 36:50.400
I would still make the same choices.

36:53.060 --> 36:54.660
But I will never laugh at you.

37:01.840 --> 37:02.840
I am sick and tired

37:04.280 --> 37:05.480
of all that weighing.

37:07.400 --> 37:08.510
I will not give up.

37:09.360 --> 37:12.110
I will not let Lejun end up like me.

37:29.920 --> 37:33.230
Princess Pingning shall enter the hall.

37:43.450 --> 37:48.020
♪ If fate is fragile,
what is right or wrong ♪

37:49.910 --> 37:54.910
♪ We only live for what we can't let go ♪

37:55.350 --> 37:58.970
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

37:58.990 --> 38:01.930
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

38:01.950 --> 38:07.670
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

38:08.300 --> 38:11.690
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

38:11.710 --> 38:14.730
♪ The heart's a cage,
but peace will break the chains ♪

38:14.750 --> 38:20.500
♪ No need to speak,
just leave it all to fate ♪

38:33.840 --> 38:37.330
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

38:37.350 --> 38:40.300
♪ The heart's a cage,
but peace will break the chains ♪

38:40.320 --> 38:47.160
♪ No need to speak,
just leave it all to fate ♪

38:52.840 --> 38:55.030
I, Li Lejun, Princess Pingning, extend

38:55.030 --> 38:56.690
my greetings to Your Majesty.

38:56.710 --> 38:57.800
Long live

38:58.550 --> 38:59.710
Your Majesties.

39:22.070 --> 39:22.840
Your Highness?

39:22.840 --> 39:24.170
Yuan Xiaoliu, come out!

39:24.280 --> 39:26.040
Yuan Xiaoliu is not in this carriage.

39:26.040 --> 39:27.970
He already boarded a ship and left.

39:30.880 --> 39:33.440
Yuan Xiaoliu, I know you are inside,
and that you're still

39:33.440 --> 39:35.960
still thinking about
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin.

39:35.960 --> 39:37.350
Her heart disease is incurable,

39:37.350 --> 39:38.810
and her days are numbered.

39:39.110 --> 39:40.040
If you leave now,

39:40.280 --> 39:42.960
you might never get to see her again
in the rest of your life.

39:42.960 --> 39:44.630
Listen up. Tonight,

39:44.630 --> 39:45.800
I've arranged a Northern Qin puppet show

39:45.800 --> 39:47.000
in Xiyue Restaurant.

39:47.320 --> 39:49.180
It is up to you whether to go or not.

39:49.680 --> 39:52.410
You'd hate to have regrets
for a lifetime, right?

40:00.400 --> 40:01.200
Yuan Xiaoliu.

40:01.390 --> 40:03.180
Mr. Yuan, do not act rashly.

40:03.550 --> 40:04.840
It's His Highness's order

40:04.840 --> 40:06.240
that you will be executed

40:06.550 --> 40:08.480
on the spot if you defy the command.

40:13.710 --> 40:16.230
All the 138 members of the Yuan clan

40:17.630 --> 40:19.160
died because of that woman.

40:19.960 --> 40:21.760
I severed ties with her long ago.

40:22.150 --> 40:24.840
Now, hearing that she is about to die,

40:25.800 --> 40:29.460
I only feel the pleasure
of having my greatest revenge fulfilled.

40:30.550 --> 40:31.920
I will never

40:32.510 --> 40:33.320
see her again.

40:33.840 --> 40:34.480
Qing Long,

40:35.360 --> 40:36.150
let's go.

40:49.590 --> 40:50.520
You really came.

40:50.920 --> 40:52.510
If Xiao Wuyi finds out about this,

40:52.510 --> 40:52.920
I will...

40:52.920 --> 40:53.650
Don't worry.

40:54.000 --> 40:56.400
I promise to save your life
with mine today.

40:56.440 --> 40:57.440
If the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin

40:57.440 --> 40:58.970
truly attempts to hurt you,

40:59.320 --> 41:00.440
I will shield you

41:00.510 --> 41:01.640
and let you go first.

41:02.400 --> 41:03.550
You have my word.

41:05.440 --> 41:07.630
Xiao Wuyi will be furious then.

41:08.440 --> 41:09.370
What did you say?

41:09.780 --> 41:10.510
Nothing.

41:11.080 --> 41:11.840
I mean,

41:12.030 --> 41:13.150
are you really planning

41:13.150 --> 41:14.800
to risk your life for the cancellation

41:14.800 --> 41:16.130
of Li Lejun's marriage?

41:16.760 --> 41:17.670
Isn't this

41:17.760 --> 41:19.490
what friends do for each other?

41:20.510 --> 41:22.030
Moved by your chivalry,

41:22.360 --> 41:25.490
I've decided to stand or fall
together with you tonight.

41:35.030 --> 41:37.030
Today is your wedding day.

41:38.110 --> 41:40.110
Prince Qi claimed to be sick
and took leave from court.

41:40.110 --> 41:42.310
Young Lord Xiao hasn't shown up either.

41:42.480 --> 41:43.630
Could it be that the two of them

41:43.630 --> 41:45.580
are dissatisfied with this marriage

41:45.580 --> 41:48.110
and are working together
to object it for you?

41:54.190 --> 41:55.450
It doesn't matter now.

42:01.800 --> 42:03.030
The auspicious hour has arrived.

42:03.030 --> 42:04.400
His Highness the Eagle King

42:04.400 --> 42:07.660
and Princess Pingning shall perform
the bowing ceremony.

42:12.230 --> 42:14.000
Eagle King, please bow.

42:16.960 --> 42:18.760
Princess Pingning, please bow.

42:24.960 --> 42:27.000
Princess Pingning, please bow.
